Two weeks after laying my mother to rest, I flew to shoot with JCrew, ironically, on her birthday. 
To shoot in a white suit (which I wore for my mother's funeral) was the sweetest homage to her. @jcrew thank you for honoring my tender heart and making this shoot one of the best of my “retired” career! You gave me reason to smile when my whole world was crumbling. Cheers to all that were involved! 🤍🕊 #injcrew
P.s. @olympiamarie you are the goat! You create the best suits for women, periodt.
Mazel, to this atrocity of a year coming to a much anticipated close! Thank you to pinot noir and friends who laughed and cried with me. 2022, you sucked. The end
“We make a lot of detours, but we’re always headed for the same destination.” Paulo Coelho

Sunflowers have deep personal meaning that’s connected to my grandmother, Bobbie Jean - who I also named a @monrowenyc brim after that Carrie Bradshaw wore on the first episode of @justlikethatmax. *shameless plug, back to the tat! 
My mother came to me in a field of sun basked sunflowers during a mediation. Sunflowers, no matter how they’re planted, always turn to face the sun, and I too, will do the same. 🌻 @ele.nyc I appreciate our late night sessions. The candy breaks and you letting me sing (off key) to the top of my lungs in your shop.

In 2017 I launched @monrowenyc from a spiritual download, vision, and money in my account. Like my (retired) 17yr modeling career, I’ve heard more nos than yeses when it comes to funding to scale the business.
•
One thing I know for certain — my grandfather, Monrowe defeated all odds during an era where being a Black man with a jazz band didn’t open doors, however, he went through the back (literally) to make a mark that still resonates present day. I have his DNA running through me and a host of ancestors championing me forward. Monrowe is not simply a brand of hats, but a story richly rooted in culture, exemplifying resiliency and empowerment. Although being an entrepreneur can be exhausting, I’m a firm believer that every ‘no’ is simply a redirection to that one yes!

@senderonosara your space is unmatched! Simplistic luxury in the middle of the jungle. Thank you for your hospitality. For my warm lemon water every morning. For reminding me to prioritize the sunset, and most of all, for connecting me to the amazing teachers and healers to assist me on my journey forward. Pura Vida 🪬

Nosara Nosara! I’m leaving Costa Rica with a full and open heart! @senderonosara thank you for being a safe haven for my journey. You have the best accommodating, kind-hearted staff, with the most aesthetically pleasing ambiance, and delicious cuisine. Thank you for teaching me to slow down and prioritize Mother Nature. To stop what I’m doing daily to behold the sunset. Thank you for bringing me back to my center and taking me deeper into my healing journey by means of plant medicine. Your physical space was the conduit that brought me to the most beautiful divine feminine souls, teachers, and healers. 
🌿
I’ve connected to my souls resonance in your tucked away jungle oasis. I’ve left pieces of my heart here so I’ll always return. Pura Vida for life!

Dear younger self, I am so proud of you! Of your fight and resiliency to recreate all narratives that aren’t in alignment with where you see yourself growing. You have an incredible assignment to carry out in this life time. The journey of walking it out will be filled with so much uncertainty and pain. Most of what you’re carrying isn’t yours. You’ll learn later in life how to set it down. There will be times you want to give up, and you will try in that effort, however, you are being guided and led even during the darkest points of the voyage. There will come a time when you’ve done all the healing, shedding, upleveling, and releasing that’s required. What is being asked of you next is to persevere and endure. During this phase, you’re learning to trust yourself while integrating. You are being redirected and sent the conduits that are going to help catapult you to the next season of life. As you grow and evolve those attachments that were linked to old versions of you will fall away, this is part of the journey. The greatest love of all is your love for self. This will become your lived experience later in life. I’m proud of you beyond measure! You’ve made it to 38! A year that will begin to make all the other years of loss, rejection, stress, lack, uncertainty, and barrenness make sense. Continue to take up all the space. You’re so deserving and worthy. Remember, you are the purpose, it isn’t something to be figured out but lived.

The latest addition to our ‘Behind The Ink” series is from Dani Evans (@danievans1) who received this piece from our founder @evakrbdk at our Havemeyer St. studio on June 3rd. 

In 2020, Dani dissolved her modeling contract in order to focus on her brand @monrowenyc — paying homage to her grandfather’s jazz roots in the American South. 

On Dani’s arm, a black hawk eagle’s wing serves as her protector, an emblem of strength and resilience. Alongside it, a crescent moon symbolizes the shadows we all walk through in life. 

#AtelierEva #FemaleFounders
I’m not on vacation, I’m home.

Jostin!!! There is absolutely no one else in Costa Rica that I would trust enough to take me on the wild, epic, adventures you have shown me. Thank you for teaching me to let go and trust myself. Your wisdom of the land, culture, and history of your people is so beautiful. At this big age, you got me out here feeling like Moana, seeing real live crocodiles and such. Thank you for lightening the load I’d been carrying. May your company, @epic_atv_adventures continue to thrive and grow as you pour into every life that you influence. You are a true wizard and genuine soul yo. “Nothing can stop you you’re all the way up!” Pura Vida 🦋
@hanaleireponty, thank you for my favorite suit! @abysseofficial 🍊

Life has a way of challenging you and pushing you past your comfort zone. If at first you don’t succeed, Jostin will keep pushing you until do! You’re incredible babe, thank you! @epic_atv_adventures @chorotegassurf. @abysseofficial thank you for my surf gear! 🏄🏾‍♀️ She’s official now!
